{
  "uid": "champy-host",
  "title": "Champy - Hôte (serveur WSL2)",
  "description": "Ressources de l'hôte qui exécute Docker (environnement WSL2) : CPU, RAM, disque, charge, réseau. Alimenté par node-exporter. Complément du dashboard « Ressources containers ».",
  "tags": [
    "champy",
    "host",
    "node-exporter"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 2,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "À propos de ce tableau de bord",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Ressources de l'hôte qui exécute Docker** (environnement WSL2), mesurées par node-exporter. En WSL2, ces valeurs reflètent les ressources *allouées à WSL* (ajustables via `.wslconfig`), c'est-à-dire ce qui est réellement disponible pour les containers, et non le matériel Windows complet.\n\n- **CPU / RAM / Disque hôte (%)** : indicateurs de saturation globale (vert/orange/rouge).\n- **Mémoire hôte (octets)** : mémoire utilisée vs totale de l'environnement WSL2.\n- **Charge CPU (load average)** : charge système sur 1/5/15 min, à comparer au nombre de cœurs WSL2.\n- **Débit réseau hôte** : trafic agrégé des interfaces.\n- **Occupation disque par filesystem** : taux de remplissage du storage Docker (`/var/lib`)."
      },
      "transparent": false
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "CPU hôte (%)",
      "description": "Pourcentage CPU utilisé sur l'hôte WSL2 (100 - idle). Vue globale de la charge processeur.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "100 - (avg(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100)",
          "legendFormat": "CPU hote (%)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 70
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 90
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "RAM hôte (%)",
      "description": "Pourcentage de RAM utilisée sur l'hôte WSL2 (basé sur MemAvailable).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "(1 - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "RAM hote (%)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 75
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 90
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Disque Docker (%)",
      "description": "Taux d'occupation du storage Docker (/var/lib, device du disque virtuel WSL). C'est ce disque qui se remplit avec les images, volumes et containers du projet.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "100 - (node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint=\"/var/lib\"} / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint=\"/var/lib\"} * 100)",
          "legendFormat": "Disque Docker (%)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 80
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 90
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Mémoire hôte (octets)",
      "description": "Mémoire utilisée et totale de l'hôte WSL2. L'écart avec le matériel Windows = ce que WSL2 ne s'est pas alloué.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 11
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "utilisee",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "node_memory_MemTotal_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "totale",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "calcs": [
            "last",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Charge CPU (load average)",
      "description": "Charge moyenne du système sur 1, 5 et 15 minutes. À comparer au nombre de cœurs alloués à WSL2.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 11
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "node_load1",
          "legendFormat": "1m",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "node_load5",
          "legendFormat": "5m",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "node_load15",
          "legendFormat": "15m",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "calcs": [
            "last",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Débit réseau hôte (octets/s)",
      "description": "Trafic réseau entrant et sortant agrégé sur les interfaces de l'hôte WSL2 (hors loopback).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{device!=\"lo\"}[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "rx {{device}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{device!=\"lo\"}[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "tx {{device}}",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "Bps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "calcs": [
            "last",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Occupation disque par filesystem (%)",
      "description": "Taux d'occupation de chaque filesystem réel de l'hôte (hors tmpfs/overlay).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 19
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "100 - (node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint=~\"/var/lib|/mnt\"} / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint=~\"/var/lib|/mnt\"} * 100)",
          "legendFormat": "{{mountpoint}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "calcs": [
            "last",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
